                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9221" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1396</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1093 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">餐饮品牌如何从地方走向全国：小吊梨汤餐饮品牌 标准化和差异化兼容的创新策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How local restaurants expand from local to national regions: Innovative strategies for standardization and differentiation compatibility of Xiaodiao Litang Catering Brands</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李杨，祁玉，安京旭，王勇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以食为喜（北京）餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">餐饮品牌；标准化；差异化；市场扩张；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">catering brands, standardization, differentiation, market expansion </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在竞争日趋白热化的餐饮行业中，餐饮品牌的市场扩张不仅是品牌发展的机会，也是提升竞争力的方式。但是，餐饮品牌想要从地方走向全国，需要面对诸多问题和挑战。如何在扩张的过程中，保持品牌传统价值和核心特色，兼顾不断变化的消费者期望和区域市场的特定需求，是餐饮品牌需要解决的难题。消费者对餐厅的口味和服务的期望提升，推动餐饮品牌一方面要保持菜品的原汁原味，一方面还要不断创新以吸引年轻消费群体。基于这样的困境，案例聚焦于小吊梨汤餐饮品牌从北京走向全国的历程，揭示了小吊梨汤如何通过标准化和差异化兼容的创新策略来应对灵活的市场变化，帮助本土品牌成功在北京以外的城市站稳脚跟。案例研究内容和结论对其它希望从地方走向全国的餐饮品牌具有宝贵的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the increasingly competitive catering industry, market expansion of catering brands is not only an opportunity for brand development, but also a way to enhance competitiveness. However, catering brands need to face many problems and challenges in order to expand from local to national regions. One of the problems is to find a balance between maintaining the traditional values and core characteristics of the brand during the expansion process and taking into account of constantly changing consumer expectations and specific needs of the regional market. Consumer expectations for the taste and service of restaurants have increased, driving catering brands to maintain the original taste of their dishes while constantly innovating to attract young consumers. Based on this dilemma, the case focuses on the expansion journey of Xiaodiao Litang from Beijing to other countries, revealing how Xiaodiao Litang responds to flexible market changes through innovative strategies of standardization and differentiation compatibility, helping local brands successfully establish a foothold in cities outside of Beijing. The content and conclusions of the case study have valuable reference value for other catering brands aiming to expand from local to national regions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销学》、《战略品牌管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST宏观环境分析理论；市场细分和市场定位理论；营销策略4P理论、身份认同理论；文化认同理论；口碑传播涟漪效应理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
